message.text:
2014 Sochi Olympic games are over! "絆 KIZUNA" among athletes, their families and audiences moved us deeply.
>>Try to find the meaning of the Kanji "絆" from below!
1. bond 2. embarrassed 3. want
http://www.anime-manga.jp/KanjiGame/Love/
「絆」の意味はどれ？オリンピックではたくさんの絆ストーリーに感動。Looking forward to see 「絆」in Sochi Paralympics too!
